description: The partial demolition and alteration of Paynes Wharf, the demolition of Borthwick Wharf, and redevelopment of the site to provide for 247 residential dwellings, 10 live/work units, B1 office use, D1 gallery and health provision, A1/A2/A3 retail and restaurant uses, in blocks ranging from three to eighteen storeys, 180 parking spaces, new road and access layout, footpaths and river path.
